txt.en: Orc tents can be found around the port of Harlond.\n\nYou should destroy Orc tents in Harlond.
'Orc encampments clutter Harlond. If we are to clear the port, we must destroy their camps. Burning their tents should send the Orcs a message to leave Harlond for good!'
Orc tents can be found around the port of Harlond.\n\nYou should destroy Orc tents in Harlond.
Aragorn will need the port of Harlond cleared if he and his men are to make landfall with haste.
